






@(1-2=c3311.1) Say to @wPN{Enlil-massu} what @wPN{Inim-Inana} says:

@(3-15=c3311.3) They told me everything and I am pleased beyond exaggeration. May the precious protective power of a lifetime; @wPN{Lugal-šu}, @wPN{Nabi-Enlil} and @wPN{Enlil-alsag}, the scholars who precede you; and @wDN{Ninimma}, your own goddess, and @wDN{Nisaba}, the lady of broad wisdom, give wisdom to you. You did not know what was written on the tablet or that the city would be unforthcoming. @wPN{Lu-gena} is sending you two shekels of silver, one garment and two sashes. Accept them. But your mother should not touch the remaining assets. It is urgent.



